column5: Very nice Jim, you must still be beaming from ear to ear
Just got back from my favorite lake to fish.  It did not disappoint again.  Here are a couple of beauties I caught in the last 2 days.   The 52 incher...   46 incher...
nice 52" man, i love it when they are so big you can't hit em all in the photo, nice couple of fish man! sounds like you had a good fishing trip
Very nice man!!    What was the pattern on those?
Beauty !!! Congrats
Wow, nice fish man! I can see that lake treats you well
Well done Jim!!! I'll be there this weekend, drop by if you're in the 'hood!
Very nice Jim!!
Awesome Jim congrats
Very nice Jim!!!  I knew I should have made a trip up for the day  Maureen
very nice aqwesome fish
Very very nice Jim! Congrats to you.
nice going
Dang Jim.   Those are two great fish.   Just a shade under two weeks and I'll be on the French chasing them.   Congrats
Good work Jim
Nice!!
Nice fish, thanks for sharing.
Those are a couple of nice ski's man good job!
Thanks for the replies everyone.
sweet catch  im starting to go into musky mode right now... havent fished em in a month... been obsessed with walleye
Great fish man!
Wow, nice pair of musky! Congrats!
Nicely done Jim!  Those West Arm Skis have eluded me for far too long.
Awesome!
There is a "FIX" for that ya know

I feel your pain Chris. I even hired (for a handshake and a smile) one of the Musky legends to get me a fish and let's just say I beat him and have keep my musky status at zero. Thanks for trying Lew we will give it another go Next Year.   Art
